				<h1>Limitations</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">Find prompts that fit your field of work</span><br>
					Example: “I am an Enterprise Communications Consultant. Please tell me 5 prompts I can ask you to benefit my daily work.”
				</p>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">Make your daily workflow more efficient</span><br>
					GWChat can generate new content, extract and summarize information from existing documents, write code, translate, and more.
				</p>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">I am still a work in progress</span><br>
					This is the first release of GWChat. Future versions will incorporate GuideWell specific information including context about members, a higher quality translation engine, document upload feature, and more.
				</p>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">Ask GWChat a general question</span><br>
					GWChat has basic knowledge about health insurance and clinical concepts, just to name a few. Example: “What is the Medicare Part D coverage gap?”
				</p>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">Contents to use</span><br>
					GWChat is an Enterprise solution for GuideWell. You can use PHI and confidential information safely and securely for your conversations and tasks.
				</p>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">Potential incorrectness</span><br>
					Please be aware that GWChat can occasionally generate incorrect information. Make sure to check the output prior to using it.
				</p>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">GWChat can help with creative tasks</span><br>
					Example: “How to encourage employees and members to get the flu shots?”
				</p>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">Chat history</span><br>
					On the left-hand panel, your chat history is available, it can be reused or deleted at any time.
				</p>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
				<p>
					<span class="title">Limited Knowledge after 2022</span><br>
					Please note that GWChat has limited knowledge of the world and events after 2022. 
				</p>
    </div>
</div>